pullRequests.body:
___This works with the latest code in cb-apply branch of apply platform___

* Based on skipResumePicker property of the application form, skip the resume picker, and go straight to the screeners.
* See this [Commit](https://github.com/cbdr/cbax-apply-platform/commit/418ac75863b13de4b4d351d66c77aaf70e3ab1d6) in apply platform (I added comments to this commit that show what was changed/why)

pullRequests.title: Front end logging alt
pullRequests.body:
Super simple interface for sending logs and metrics to the [server-side proxy](https://github.com/cbdr/cbax-apply-platform/tree/front-end-logging). 

This is an alternative to an existing angular loggly module (see front-end-logging branch). But perhaps we will use the features of a the existing logger and it's worth the extra weight/dependencies.

Thoughts???
